docs {
  # Missing Label IDs - Error Case

  ## Test Scenario
  Send request without label_ids field to test validation.

  ## Expected Behavior
  - Status: 400 Bad Request
  - Error message about required labels

  ## Expected Response
  ```json
  {
    "status": false,
    "result": "Error assigning multiple labels: Label ids are required"
  }
  ```

  ## Test Coverage
  - Required field validation
  - Missing array parameter
}
